{"id": "1222535263327096933", "channel_id": "1222535263327096933", "type": 0, "author_id": "1220335168502628405", "author_name": "zhouvanc", "author_bot": false, "content": "写在最前：水平有限所以只发了我＆朋友认为手感很赞的阵容，欢迎讨论，敬请斧正\n\n\n配队：拉蒙娜（普），雷娅，艾继丝，潘狄娅\n\n配置要点：神王再衍化艾，埋骨地娜（精英关卖死抗→升狂气快速开大），死亡的剖析潘（借高配最宜，uid：100098886）\n\n路线：先走右侧，一路向上，踩传送到地图左侧，向左打一场普战，进商店，进精英，通常在精英关可以卖死抗加快输出速度（穿埋骨地艾也可，意义同上），之后随便走就可以，认为黑印足够的情况下可以空1-2关普战不刷（比如较早拿到翠玉拓印or开局石碑/伶牙俐齿）\n\n造物：力量造物，力量造物，还是力量造物（算力造物/刻印多的情况下也推荐买原型电池，狂气回转飞快）\n\n效果展示：", "timestamp": "2024-03-27T13:18:40.384000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1222535263549653023", "filename": "-66901ebee1e0894e.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 124969, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222535263327096933/1222535263549653023/-66901ebee1e0894e.jpg?ex=69fb3fb0&is=69f9ee30&hm=4118a631a91a5a158d9377d1cd2f030ab538a421181d7dc0e56b5a50431f9642&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1222535263327096933", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "简易版【燃烧的群宴】活动尾关速杀攻略：", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1222556596161216674", "channel_id": "1222556596161216674", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果你對自己隊伍的道中強度非常有自信，請大膽的選擇第三種碾壓過去。\n\n然而如果你的隊伍是道中強度堪憂，或者越級打副本，那麼第一二種走法會比較適合你。\n第一種是開局直接打小怪，不幸觸發死抗的話就先走事件，再從傳送門出來後直接吃回血，接著才拿黑印。\n第二種則是還算有餘裕，剩個一兩百血先踩燙地板再拿黑印，最後回血。", "timestamp": "2024-03-27T14:43:26.528000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1222556596366872607", "filename": "1222548687952281691remix-17115489723202.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 323952, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222556596161216674/1222556596366872607/1222548687952281691remix-17115489723202.png?ex=69fb538e&is=69fa020e&hm=db9864ee7aa179db53400578635e8594aab7fa386c8660974b72218d703beb27&"}, {"id": "1222556596702285834", "filename": "1222548687952281691remix-17115487721862.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 329770, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222556596161216674/1222556596702285834/1222548687952281691remix-17115487721862.png?ex=69fb538e&is=69fa020e&hm=6845dc6e75fe95b901e23ca6a794261abd24b8be3a26767fe58ab4938a5c6072&"}, {"id": "1222556596983300237", "filename": "20240327_2220312.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 108725, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222556596161216674/1222556596983300237/20240327_2220312.jpg?ex=69fb538e&is=69fa020e&hm=53f47533b26c0e893f09ec116e366538c11593f91545228fea90d4aa3cb24039&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1222556596161216674", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "簡單的活動本尾關開局走法", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1181143392739147778"]}
